author: WCAX News
title: Dunne to back Bernie
text:
WHITE RIVER JUNCTION, Vt. - Democratic gubernatorial hopeful Matt Dunne says he plans to stand behind Bernie Sanders.
Dunne is the first of the three Democrats vying for the governors seat to come out with an endorsement in the presidential race. The former state senator and Google Executive says Sanders performance in last week's debate cemented his decision.
